title: False Ceiling
description: Providing and fixing suspended false ceiling which includes providing and fixing GI perimeter channels of size 0.35 mm thick having one flange of 20 mm and another flange of 30 mm and web of 27 mm along the perimeter of the ceiling, screw fixed to brick wall/ partition with help of nylon sleeves and screws, at 610 mm centers. Finally, the boards are to be joined and finished so as to have a flush look which includes finishing the tapered and square edges of the board with joining compound. paper tape etc : Saint gobain Gyproc/India Gypsum make 12.55mm thic
